'''Andrea Campagnolo''' (born [[17 June]] [[1978]] in [[Bassano del Grappa]], [[Province of Vicenza]]) is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[Football (soccer)|football]] [[goalkeeper]] currently playing for [[Serie A]] club [[Reggina Calcio|Reggina]].

*Campagnolo is currently 1st choice goalkeeper at [[Reggina Calcio|Reggina]].

